        "cooked": "<p>The <strong>2015 Pierre-Yves Colin-Morey Saint-Aubin Le Banc</strong> glistens in the glass in a most inviting way. There\u2019s just the right amount of smoky mineral reduction. It is richly fruited, loaded with citrus of all persuasion. It possesses a crystalline quality and is direct, intense and finishes so fresh and bright.</p>",
