        "username": "Jerry_Hey",
        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/jerry_hey/{size}/1033_2.png",
        "created_at": "2020-03-12T16:29:23.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I haven\u2019t had the '15 Banc from PYCM but the en Remilly was delicious last time I had it.  I did try the '18 Banc at the Atherton tasting and thought it was one of the better wines that day.</p>",
